</taxonomicName>
), Fig. 12.
</paragraph>
<caption id="7BFF664EFF870167EC866D4CE499006E" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5422327" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5422327" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5422327/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" startId="19.[136,229,1820,1842]" targetBox="[291,1297,991,1793]" targetPageId="19">
<paragraph id="2F3F36C6FF870167EC866D4CE499006E" blockId="19.[136,1451,1820,1878]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
